{"tw": {"3087180": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Stellar Dream - Part 1", "steam_appid": 3087180, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [3878390], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>故事</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Stellar Dream（星夢）中，你將置身於一場科幻冒險。在這場冒險中，你的決定不只會影響你的未來，也會決定人類的命運。作為你殖民地的這艘船將邁向為人類尋找嶄新殖民地的旅程。偵查人員已經選好了三個最適合的備選家園；然而，通訊在這之後被切斷了。你的任務是帶回偵查人員、找到一個優良的殖民地，並與外星生物建立外交關係。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索三個截然不同的星球</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個可供探索的星球都有自身獨特的環境和人形外星人。你是否能克服惡劣條件，生存下來並勝利完成任務？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有意義的關係</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087180/extras/495a132cf093d3dbfbe49458051da5bb.poster.avif?t=1773234647\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087180/extras/495a132cf093d3dbfbe49458051da5bb.webm?t=1773234647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087180/extras/495a132cf093d3dbfbe49458051da5bb.mp4?t=1773234647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打算如何處理所面對的任何情況，想成為怎樣的人，一切都取決於你。你會獲得愛情嗎？還是仇恨？你會結交朋友，找到真愛，建立你的後宮，亦或是沉溺於慾望？全都取決於你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_para