<li><strong>處理器:</strong> 2.0 Ghz 64-bit Intel-compatible<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 2 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> OpenGL 3.0<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 3 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "developers": ["Winterlook Games"], "publishers": ["Winterlook Games"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 26800, "final": 26800, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 268"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 29, "description": "Steam 交換卡片"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 11 月 6 日"}}}}, "us": {"3087180": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Stellar Dream - Part 1", "steam_appid": 3087180, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [3878390], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stellar Dream puts you in the middle of sci-fi adventure where your choices shape your destiny and the fate of humanity. The colony ship was set out to find new worlds for human colonization and their scouts left to the  most suitable candidates, but the communication with them has been lost. Your task is to bring the scouts home, find a suitable home for the colony and establish diplomatic ties with alien life forms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore distinct planets </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every planet available for exploration has its unique nature and humanoid aliens. Will you be able to survive in this unfamiliar environment and succeed in your mission? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><st